Taking a page from JIRA's recent "why can't I see this field?" tool, it would be great for Confluence to have a "why can't this user see/edit/restrict this page?"

This is a common topic that comes up in Support. Administrators will add a page restriction to a page, not realizing that this only _takes away_ existing space permissions. If the user does not have space permissions to begin with, nothing happens, since page restrictions do not _grant_ any permissions (essentially, this is the scenario described in https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONF-7089)

This tool would help clarify the problem for customers and also cut down support load.

